<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/myArticles.css">
</head>
<body>

    
    <div class="col-12" >
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-10" >
                <div class="article-info col-12 mt-3 px-0 py-0">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-10 ">
                            <h5 class="article-title">security of IOT</h5>
                            <div class="abstract padding-0 px-5 col-12">
                                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Placeat illo, ab eligendi porro doloremque quas aperiam minima consectetur laboriosam nisi quia perspiciatis sunt earum accusamus ex ipsum. Ea, eveniet totam? Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fugit, dolores distinctio voluptatum, veniam quia neque sit, iure similique placeat nam vero iusto nulla error? Distinctio illum ipsa quibusdam obcaecati consectetur.
